Key Match Events: Attys Christopher scored the opening goal for Haiti in the 40th minute
Duckens Nazon scored a header in the 59th minute
Duckens Nazon scored his second goal in the 75th minute
Mikael Cantave scored in the 77th minute
Duckens Nazon completed his hat-trick in the 82nd minute
Mikael Cantave secured his double in the 85th minute
Pre-Game Insights: French coach Sébastien Migné revealed his starting 11 with several changes
Post-Match Reflections: This victory consolidates the Grenadiers' leadership in Group C
Note that goalkeeper Jhony Placide got his first clean sheet in this group stage
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was the second Group match of League B of the 2024 Nations League (CNL) of the Confederation of North, Central American and Caribbean Countries (CONCACAF)
Others: The match was played at the 'Estadio Centroamericano' in Mayagüez
The upcoming match schedule for Haiti includes games against Aruba on October 10, 2024, and October 14, 2024
